# Files copied into every git worktree Claude Code creates for subagents.
# Only files that are BOTH gitignored AND listed here are copied — keeps
# secrets out of commits while making sure worktree subagents can:
#   - connect to local Supabase (NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL + keys)
#   - mint gateway tokens (SUPABASE_SECRET_KEY, ENCRYPTION_KEY)
#   - hit Anthropic / SF / Slack / GitHub for real-proxy tests
# Anything needed by `pnpm dev`, `pnpm supabase`, or vitest integration tests
# that's NOT committed should land here.

.env.local
.env
